{"tid":2353691,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"捕捉周子瑜跨年夜「奇蹟美照」一轉身「超殺眼神」網友瘋了","createTime":"2021-01-05T02:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T16:37:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7982ca0e5b50ed7382b295b82e1bf6b867c07d1b","tid":2353691,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"南韓超人氣女團TWICE去年年底登上許多大型典禮，每一次出場舞蹈、造型都成為焦點，尤其是跨年在韓國「2020 MBC歌謠大祭典」，其中台灣成員周子瑜穿著白色連身短裙，無袖露出纖細手臂，超高馬尾造型讓PTT網友嗨翻，現在更有一張「奇蹟美照」流出，許多韓國網友看了都大讚超級漂亮，紛紛在網路上瘋傳！<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/04/2969385-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2F2969385-PH.jpg&h=358b59b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲周子瑜跨年高馬尾造型美翻。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/04/2969386-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2F2969386-PH.jpg&h=ac693fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓女團TWICE在去年年底一連登上了KBS歌謠大祝祭、SBS歌謠大戰，還有MBC歌謠大祭典等等，陪著粉絲們開心跨年，其中MBC歌謠大祭典中，台灣成員周子瑜高馬尾的新造型引起大家關注，推爆PTT留言狂讚她：「高馬尾很美 」、「子瑜這造型好看」、「TWICE也太早出場，子瑜好美！！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/04/2969387-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2F2969387-PH.jpg&h=6de7e073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜《Cry For Me》宣傳照。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE表演了〈I Can't Stop Me （Disco Ver.）〉、〈MORE &amp; MORE〉、〈Cry For Me〉等今年的新歌，其中在換上黑白色系服裝表演時，子瑜的被攝影師拍到一張「奇蹟美照」，綁著高馬尾、穿著一身白色連身短裙，無袖露出纖細手臂，超高馬尾造型，一手插腰一手舉起，略為冷豔的表情加上性感的服裝，許多韓國網友看了都大讚超級漂亮，就像洋娃娃般精緻美麗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/twice_satzumo/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftwice_satzumo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuORPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=d4dc6150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/twice_satzumo/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n▲攝影師拍下周子瑜奇蹟美照，在網路上瘋傳。"},{"pid":"6759f0718fdd94a18150006249180f1afb13d8d7","tid":2353691,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"暴動了..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e8d34ab63a681c27476be678822bcc2a150a11","tid":2353691,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"周老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbbd78d77184853ea14dd8cde41ff5e12deafc8","tid":2353691,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6759f0718fdd94a18150006249180f1afb13d8d7","tid":2353691,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"暴動了..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"我都暴動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0ff8c73fa34458f895149e9c3b9780f24ffcd9","tid":2353691,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e8d34ab63a681c27476be678822bcc2a150a11","tid":2353691,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"周老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"周老母是好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37527bc07eb12cd3bb072a3ebb68544e53d2ed8d","tid":2353691,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dbbd78d77184853ea14dd8cde41ff5e12deafc8","tid":2353691,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6759f0718fdd94a18150006249180f1afb13d8d7","tid":2353691,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"暴動了..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:46:15.000Z"